title: Did Bayden's birthday video show without a mask in 2020?
subtitle: A viral tweet with a video that says, "They tell us to stay away from society and wear a mask! But as you can see... they're not! They're all lies to control us!"
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: President-elect Joe Biden's video was shown to celebrate his birthday with a bunch of maskless people in 2020.
